name: r-gfdsurv
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.1.0' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-gfdsurv
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/GFDsurv_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/GFDsurv/GFDsurv_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 4996311dbaa240d536798b17cd87bf2e6c2d870307ab61209df2e5f4fdfecacf

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-mass >=7.3_53
    - r-gridextra >=2.3
    - r-magic >=1.5_9
    - r-plyr >=1.8.6
    - r-shiny >=1.5.0
    - r-shinyjs >=2.0.0
    - r-shinythemes >=1.1.2
    - r-survival >=3.2_7
    - r-survminer >=0.4.8
    - r-tippy >=0.1.0
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-mass >=7.3_53
    - r-gridextra >=2.3
    - r-magic >=1.5_9
    - r-plyr >=1.8.6
    - r-shiny >=1.5.0
    - r-shinyjs >=2.0.0
    - r-shinythemes >=1.1.2
    - r-survival >=3.2_7
    - r-survminer >=0.4.8
    - r-tippy >=0.1.0

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('GFDsurv')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('GFDsurv')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/PhilippSteinhauer/GFDsurv
  license: GPL-3.0-or-later
  summary: 'Implemented are three Wald-type statistic and respective permuted versions for null
    hypotheses formulated in terms of cumulative hazard rate functions, medians and
    the concordance measure, respectively, in the general framework of survival factorial
    designs with possibly heterogeneous survival and/or censoring distributions, for
    crossed designs with an arbitrary number of factors and nested designs with up to
    three factors. Ditzhaus, Dobler and Pauly (2020) <doi:10.1177/0962280220980784>
    Ditzhaus, Janssen, Pauly (2020) <arXiv: 2004.10818v2> Dobler and Pauly (2019) <doi:10.1177/0962280219831316>.'
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
